---
// WhyClientsTrustUs section - displays core credibility drivers with 2x2 card grid
---

<section class="why-clients-trust-us">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="trust-content">
            <h2 class="heading-lg">Why Clients Trust Us</h2>

            <div class="trust-cards">
                <div class="trust-card">
                    <h3>Independent, vendor-neutral guidance</h3>
                    <p>No technology bias, no vendor relationships, no hidden agendas. Our recommendations are grounded in your strategic objectives and technical realities, not product portfolio incentives.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="trust-card">
                    <h3>Deep technical expertise translated into business risk and opportunity</h3>
                    <p>We bridge the gap between technical architecture and business impact. Complex systems become clear. Trade-offs get quantified. Risk becomes actionable.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="trust-card">
                    <h3>Executive-ready communication for leadership and investors</h3>
                    <p>Technical findings translated for boards and C-suite. No jargon. Clear implications. Decision-ready context that informs strategy and allocation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="trust-card">
                    <h3>Practical shovel-ready initiatives given real operational constraints</h3>
                    <p>Every recommendation accounts for budget, timeline, and team capacity. Roadmaps that actually happen. Next steps teams can execute.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Component styles following design system patterns */
    .why-clients-trust-us {
        padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(245, 245, 245, 0) 0%, var(--bg-light-alt) 15%, var(--bg-light-alt) 85%, rgba(245, 245, 245, 0) 100%);
        position: relative;
    }

    .trust-content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .heading-lg {
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .trust-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: var(--gap-extra-wide);
    }

    .trust-card {
        padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
        background: rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: all var(--transition-normal);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .trust-card:hover {
        background: rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.08);
        border-color: rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.2);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.1);
    }

    .trust-card h3 {
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
        font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
        color: var(--text-light-primary);
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .trust-card p {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        color: var(--text-light-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
        flex-grow: 1;
    }

    /* Dark theme support */
    :global(html.dark-theme) .why-clients-trust-us {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0) 0%, var(--bg-dark) 15%, var(--bg-dark) 85%, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0) 100%);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .trust-card {
        background: rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.05);
        border-color: rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.15);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .trust-card:hover {
        background: rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.12);
        border-color: rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.25);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .trust-card h3 {
        color: var(--text-dark-primary);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .trust-card p {
        color: var(--text-dark-secondary);
    }

    /* Responsive design */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .trust-cards {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: var(--gap-wide);
        }

        .trust-card {
            padding: var(--spacing-xl);
        }

        .trust-card h3 {
            font-size: var(--text-base);
        }

        .trust-card p {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .why-clients-trust-us {
            padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
        }

        .heading-lg {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
        }

        .trust-cards {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: var(--gap-normal);
        }

        .trust-card {
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
        }

        .trust-card h3 {
            font-size: var(--text-base);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
        }

        .trust-card p {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .why-clients-trust-us {
            padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
        }

        .heading-lg {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
        }

        .trust-cards {
            gap: var(--gap-normal);
        }

        .trust-card {
            padding: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .trust-card h3 {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
        }

        .trust-card p {
            font-size: var(--text-tiny);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    }
</style>
